{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"正常模式","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Sloppy_mode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>因为翻译原因，正常模式也被翻译为——马虎模式/稀松模式/懒散模式</p>\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/ECMAScript\">ECMAScript</a> 5 以及其后续的版本可以选择性的使用一种新模式——严格模式 (<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Strict_mode\">strict mode</a>)，这种严格模式在多个方面改变了 JavaScript 的语义，从而使得当出现问题时我们更好的理解到底发生了什么。</p>\n<p>常见的，非严格模式——平时我们会称之为正常模式 (**sloppy mode)，**这并不是一个官方说法，但是你会经常见到如上的一些说法，其意义就是指代非严格模式，即正常模式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>\"<a href=\"http://speakingjs.com/es5/ch07.html#strict_mode\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Strict Mode</a>\"，第七章 (\"JavaScript Syntax\")，《Speaking <em>JavaScript》</em></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"因为翻译原因，正常模式也被翻译为——马虎模式/稀松模式/懒散模式","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Sloppy mode","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Modo poco riguroso — Sloppy","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Sloppy mode","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Sloppy モード","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Sloppy mode","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Грязный режим","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/sloppy_mode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/sloppy_mode/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Sloppy_mode","title":"正常模式"}],"pageTitle":"正常模式 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}